Title: In the Rough
Plot: When a case from ten years is re-opened, Allison finds herself in a chaotic situation. Things continue to get messier when Allison finds out that the convicted man is innocent, and that someone she knows and trusts may have been involved in his framing.
GuestStars: Kathy Baker, Bruce Gray, Paul Adelstein, Dean Norris, Samantha Quan, Evan Parke, Paul Norwood, Mary Strong, John Eric Montana, Daniel von Lennep, Todd Malta
